Collections.rule:
Individual:
	@C*(mm:append("_Result_", @A*))
Types:
	'Acceleration Result'
Facts:
	'has_x_acceleration' @E*(xsd:float),
	'has_y_acceleration' @F*(xsd:float),
	'has_z_acceleration' @G*(xsd:float)
Annotations:
	rdfs:comment "This is the acceleration result @A* measured at @H*"

Individual:
	@C*(mm:append("_Observation_", @A*))
Types:
	'Acceleration Observation'
Facts:
	'made by sensor' @C*,
	'observed property' VGR_1_Crane_Jib_Acceleration,
	'used procedure' @I*,
	'result time' @H*(xsd:dateTime),
	'has_result' @C*(mm:append("_Result_", @A*))
Annotations:
	rdfs:comment "This is the acceleration observation @A* from the sensor @C* measured at @H*"
